52Data mapFile(const char* path)
53{
54 auto file = FileSystem::openFile(path, FileSystem::FileOpenMode::Read);
55 if (!FileSystem::isHandleValid(file))
56 return { };
57 auto size = FileSystem::fileSize(file);
58 if (!size) {
59 FileSystem::closeFile(file);
60 return { };
61 }
62 return adoptAndMapFile(file, 0, *size);
63}

70Data adoptAndMapFile(FileSystem::PlatformFileHandle handle, size_t offset, size_t size)
71{
72 if (!size) {
73 FileSystem::closeFile(handle);
74 return Data::empty();
75 }
76 bool success;
77 FileSystem::MappedFileData mappedFile(handle, FileSystem::FileOpenMode::Read, FileSystem::MappedFileMode::Private, success);
78 if (!success) {
79 FileSystem::closeFile(handle);
80 return { };
81 }
82
83 return Data::adoptMap(WTFMove(mappedFile), handle);
84}

86SHA1::Digest computeSHA1(const Data& data, const Salt& salt)
87{
88 SHA1 sha1;
89 sha1.addBytes(salt.data(), salt.size());
90 data.apply([&sha1](const uint8_t* data, size_t size) {
91 sha1.addBytes(data, size);
92 return true;
93 });

95 SHA1::Digest digest;
96 sha1.computeHash(digest);
